1
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,280
My Lady.

2
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,400
It's you!

3
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:51,159
You stole my husband on our wedding night,

4
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,879
slaughtered the Liu family,

5
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,280
and killed my husband!

6
00:01:57,879 --> 00:01:58,640
Cang Feng,

7
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,439
how dare you!

8
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:01,599
My Lady,

9
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,519
you once said

10
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,400
you wanted freedom.

11
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:10,599
How dare you!

12
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:12,599
The Liu family has always been a bunch of good-for-nothings!

13
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:13,919
Follow me.

14
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,240
Escape from the capital,

15
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:20,719
and you can do whatever you want with me.

16
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:28,560
You're just a dog kicked out of my family.

17
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:30,560
How dare you touch me?

18
00:02:31,759 --> 00:02:32,520
Monster.

19
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,439
Brother.

20
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,840
Someone broke into the forbidden area.

21
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:02,759
Handle it properly according to the rules.

22
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,599
Leave no traces.

23
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,280
She's inquiring about your whereabouts.

24
00:03:21,599 --> 00:03:22,639
Behind is a cliff.

25
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:23,520
You can't escape.

26
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:25,199
I'm just asking for directions.

27
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,680
You've got the wrong person.

28
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:28,719
Still lying?

29
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:30,240
Take her to the boss.

30
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:32,319
Let's go.

31
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:38,879
[The plan worked.]

32
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,879
[The boss is nowhere to be found.]

33
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:44,680
[I have to expose myself and let them take me in.]

34
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:47,520
[Negotiate first,]

35
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,479
[then act accordingly.]

36
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:20,800
Who are you?

37
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:23,920
I'm Jiang Yue.

38
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,639
And you?

39
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:31,439
You're just a dog I kicked out of the house.

40
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,120
You don't recognize me?

41
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,839
Now I do.

42
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:41,439
Let me go.

43
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:44,399
If we're going to talk, it should be on equal footing.

44
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:51,879
It's not her.

45
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:55,839
I'm a wildlife biologist.

46
00:04:56,519 --> 00:04:58,120
I heard there were wolves nearby,

47
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,399
so I came to observe.

48
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,800
You smell like a dagger.

49
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,439
You stupid hunter,

50
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:07,079
disguising yourself as prey.

51
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,759
Then you must bear

52
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:17,199
the consequence of being eaten.

53
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,040
Don't touch me.

54
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,120
She looks exactly the same,

55
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:49,360
and has the same hobbies.

56
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:53,240
But she didn't recognize you.

57
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,079
She broke into Black Rock Island.

58
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,720
I'm afraid she has other purposes.

59
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,480
The moon is full tonight.

60
00:06:01,199 --> 00:06:02,360
All staff are under curfew.

61
00:06:04,399 --> 00:06:05,639
Don't let any news

62
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:07,560
of beasts coming out.

63
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:08,439
Yes.

64
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,759
What about Li,

65
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,000
no,

66
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,079
Jiang Yue,

67
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:16,480
who escaped?

68
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,360
She can't escape.

69
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,920
[Sixteen years ago,]

70
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:39,519
[my mom disappeared on this island.]

71
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:41,959
Mom.

72
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,680
Mom, where are you?

73
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,560
Mom.

74
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:49,160
Mom.

75
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:50,600
I can't escape.

76
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,360
I need to get close to the island owner

77
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:55,199
and figure out everything.

78
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,240
It's too early

79
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,360
to apologize.

80
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,800
The door is locked.

81
00:07:42,079 --> 00:07:43,680
I can't jump out of the window.

82
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,519
There must be an access card.

83
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,519
Where is it?

84
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,600
Where are you going?

85
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,920
[His hearing is better than a dog's.]

86
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,759
[I can't get out.]

87
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,120
[I have to fight him head-on.]

88
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,080
[How come he doesn't seem injured?]

89
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,879
[I clearly stabbed him.]

90
00:08:40,279 --> 00:08:41,399
What are you looking at?

91
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,440
There's nothing to see.

92
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,080
You want me to untie you?

93
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:12,600
As the lord of Black Rock Island,

94
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:14,240
you love to play the prisoner game.

95
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,840
If word gets out,

96
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,559
people will laugh at you.

97
00:09:18,799 --> 00:09:20,519
You walked right into this.

98
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:22,159
Speak up,

99
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,200
what do you know?

100
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,759
Your name is Lu Zhiyu,

101
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:32,639
with a mysterious background and plenty of money,

102
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:35,120
but no one knows what business you're in.

103
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:36,799
I assume

104
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:38,320
it's something shady.

105
00:09:40,519 --> 00:09:41,600
Is this all the information

106
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,399
you've spent so much to uncover?

107
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,559
It's worthless.

108
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:47,240
Doesn't matter.

109
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:48,679
Seeing you

110
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,600
is my ultimate goal.

111
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,759
I'm interested in wild animals.

112
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:58,639
I want to build an observation station

113
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,519
on your land.

114
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:00,720
No.

115
00:10:01,799 --> 00:10:02,399
Why?

116
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:04,840
Waste of time.

117
00:10:16,919 --> 00:10:18,080
In the jungle,

118
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:21,159
you must follow the law of the jungle.

119
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,240
Here,

120
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:27,360
human power is insignificant.

121
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:33,440
If you don't want to be a midnight snack for wolves,

122
00:10:38,039 --> 00:10:39,480
just stay at home.

123
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:48,480
What do you want to do tonight?

124
00:10:51,279 --> 00:10:52,519
I'm not afraid of beasts.

125
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,559
Take me to see

126
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:57,240
how they hunt.

127
00:12:00,399 --> 00:12:01,399
Monster.

128
00:12:03,759 --> 00:12:04,639
Monster.

129
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,600
I'm a monster.

130
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,039
I have no companions.
